 Transport boats surrounded by water hyacinth, with evacuation machine behind them at Ebute Jetty, Ikorodu  Deelen said this during a visit to the Ministry of Transportation. According to him, Lagos and the Netherlands share a lot of similarities in terms of population, size and closeness to the coast.  He disclosed that the waterways in his country are dredged yearly to ensure smooth movement on water.
   
